{
  "stem": "734.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "The studio was located in a corner building, at an intersection, [NON-ENGLISH] Main Street and a side street, right across from a courthouse.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the side street had a gate, where you could, let's say, drive in or enter with a vehicle or whatever, right, into the courtyard.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that window, at which I sat, was facing that gate.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So that, from that window, I could see when Lech would arrive.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He would-- he would park the car in front of that gate, so that I could see it from the window.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And as soon as I see-- as soon as I saw the car, I was told, slowly, take your time, don't rush, don't carry anything with you, don't take anything.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Just take your coat.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Have your toothbrush.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Don't take anything, whatsoever, no suitcases, no boxes, no packages.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And walk through the courtyard into the car.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Somebody will open the car for you from inside.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You hop in, and you're gone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Because I worked with the other two people, colleagues, Jews at the studio, and the problem was that, as soon as I noticed-- of course, that day I was totally restless, because I knew that was-- this was it.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "This was the day I was going to be rescued.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you can imagine the anticipation, anxiety, all that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It really worked on me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then all the rumors about liquidation of the ghetto were already known.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we didn't know how long it's gonna be, how long-- how much longer are we going to be around.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What are they going to do with us?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What else is left?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What options are there?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And sure enough, around 5 o'clock in the afternoon, it was already getting dark, after dusk.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I noticed a car.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
